    <div class='testimonial'>
        <%= cl_image_tag('testimonial1.png', class: 'image-circle')%>
      <p><i>'One of my five year goals is to complete one Ironman Triathlon and finish in the first 100!'</i></p>
      <p>Sandra, 28, doesn't know how to swim</p>
    </div>
    <div class='testimonial'>
    <%= cl_image_tag('testimonial2.png', class: 'image-circle')%>
      <p><i>'This year, I want to save up 5000 Euro's as part of my larger financial 5-year goal of buying an appartment!'</i></p>
      <p>Mike, 31, has 50k in student debt</p>
    </div>
    <div class='testimonial'>
    <%= cl_image_tag('testimonial3.png', class: 'image-circle')%>
      <p><i>'This quarter I want to research 10 towns by the sea and make plans to visit them. My 5 year goal is to live by the sea!'</i></p>
      <p>Hanna, 25, is allergic to saltwater</p>
    </div>
    </div>
  <div class='link'>
    <%= link_to 'Find inspiration', '/inspiration', class: 'btn btn-red inspiration' %>
  </div>
</div>
